Wathoni has disclosed how she got pregnant as a virgin at 23. During her wager task, Wathoni revealed that she got pregnant at 23 without having sex. Thursday’s wager was done as a tribute by Housemates to their heroes and she chose her son as her hero. Speaking of her experience as a virgin mother, the single mother of one said she adopted her father’s name for her son because she serves as parents for the young boy. “My son is my hero, I love him so much. In fact, I do not allow people to beat him. We do everything together, from Yoga to taking pictures.  “He bears my surname, Anyasi, because I’m his mother and father. He is my shining star,” she said. She however disclosed how she got pregnant without penetration. “I was a virgin till 23. That day, I was with the guy in question. At that time, I was ovulating but I didn’t know so I was not bothered about it. “He is the kind of guy that gets turned on by seeing a vagina. So, all he did was to rub his penis on my vagina and ejaculate. There was no penetration. That was it.”